  "texts": [
    "In MLM, a random fraction of tokens of the input sequence is masked (i.e.",
    "replaced by the MASK token).",
    "The model then attempts to predict the original value of the masked tokens, based on the context provided by the other, non-masked tokens in the sequence.",
    "This procedure can be performed in a fully unsupervised fashion.",
    "It is different to next-word prediction, which is inherently directional, thus limiting context learning."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}